import React from 'react'
import './app.scss'
import {BrowserRouter as Router , Route,Rou  } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './Pages/Home'
import AddtoCart from './components/Cart/AddtoCart'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Route exact path='/'>
        <Home />
      </Route>
      <Route path='/cart'>
        <AddtoCart />
      </Route>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
